, our results show\nthat the nature of the phase transition can change as well, shifting the ratio\nof the quark-antiquark and quark-quark interactions to higher values in the OPT\ncase as compared to the LN approximation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 May 2017 02:34:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Sep 2017 15:11:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-05"}
