-sections 4-10 orders of magnitude below current direct detection\nexperimental limits. Similarly, NS-imploding dark matter as the source of fast\nradio bursts can be tested at $2 \\sigma$ confidence once 20 bursts are located\nin host galaxies by radio arrays like CHIME and HIRAX.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 May 2017 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2018 18:30:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-28"}
